-warcraft-back-chinese-players-after?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中美关系：美国国务院官员解释北京如何冒着跨越与俄罗斯“红线”的风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258441/china-us-relations-american-state-department-official-explains-how-beijing-risks-crossing-red-line?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国国务院二号人物库尔特·坎贝尔（Kurt Campbell）呼应北京的“红线”和“核心利益”措辞，以标明华盛顿的战略利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258441/china-us-relations-american-state-department-official-explains-how-beijing-risks-crossing-red-line?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着“低空经济”的兴起，中国第一架电动垂直起降飞机获批生产</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258401/china-clears-first-evtol-aircraft-production-low-altitude-economy-takes-wing?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国已批准生产首款电动垂直起降飞行器，巩固了其在快速扩张的低空有人和无人驾驶飞行领域的进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3258401/china-clears-first-evtol-aircraft-production-low-altitude-economy-takes-wing?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美菲日军事关系真能保护地区安全吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/asia-opinion/article/3258216/can-us-philippine-japanese-military-ties-really-protect-regional-security?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>日本、菲律宾和美国将于本月举行历史性峰会，以在中国海军强国复兴之际深化军事合作。随着台湾和南海紧张局势加剧，三边安全安排可能会强化亚洲的零和地缘政治。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 01:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/asia-opinion/article/3258216/can-us-philippine-japanese-military-ties-really-protect-regional-security?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>从肝脏到肾脏：中国科学家在猪器官移植用于人体方面取得了又一个里程碑</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258390/liver-kidney-chinese-scientists-pass-another-milestone-pig-organ-transplants-humans?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一组科学家成功地将经过基因编辑的猪器官移植