.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258435/japanese-pm-fumio-kishida-talks-tech-cooperation-us-state-visit-begins?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>岸田文雄表示，在半导体、人工智能、量子计算和生物技术等领域，随着这两个盟友努力制衡中国，“两国增强韧性变得越来越重要”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258435/japanese-pm-fumio-kishida-talks-tech-cooperation-us-state-visit-begins?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>新法律针对中国人，教授和学生对佛罗里达州说“不”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258409/professors-students-say-no-florida-new-law-targets-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>去年生效的这项法律要求学院和大学在雇用非美国公民或绿卡持有者的中国人或与他们一起工作之前必须获得批准。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 18:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3258409/professors-students-say-no-florida-new-law-targets-chinese?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言抗议在美国虐待中国人的“每一起事件”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258389/china-vows-protest-every-single-incident-mistreatment-chinese-arrivals-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国大使馆指责美国边境当局采取高压手段，自2021年7月以来遣返了数百名中国公民。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258389/china-vows-protest-every-single-incident-mistreatment-chinese-arrivals-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>96岁风洞先驱于鸿儒因“做了别人不敢做的事”而荣获中国年度人物之一</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258418/96-year-old-wind-tunnel-pioneer-yu-hongru-honoured-one-chinas-people-year-doing-what-others-dare-not?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这位资深航空航天工程师在中央电视台主办的颁奖典礼上被形容为“隐藏的龙”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3258418/96-year-old-wind-tunnel-pioneer-yu-hongru-honoured-one-chinas-people-year-doing-what-others-dare-not?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></ite